To modify existing pod using definition yaml file
>kubectl apply -f pod.YAML

To modify existing ReplicaSet using definition yaml file
>kubectl replace -f replica.yaml

To modify existing ReplicaSet using replicaset name
kubectl edit replicasets.apps replicaset-name 

To modify existing deplyment using deplyment.yaml file
kubectl apply -f deplyment.YAML

To modify existing deplyment using deplyment name
kubectl edit deplyment.apps deplyment-name
